name: Global Resell Business
overview:
About Founded in 2006, due to its solid relationship with world well-known original manufacturer in China, Global Resell Business is dedicatedly to provide sourcing & solutions to support retailers, manufacturers and distributors in global scale. As a leading laptop parts sourcing channel, Global Resell Business is able to provide wide range of in-stocks laptop parts including LCD panel, HDD, Keyboard, AC Adapter, Batteries, Hard Drive, Optical Disk Drive, Memory, Motherboard, CPU and IC components with original manufacture direct source and competitive price.
